#ROOM
Vnum     37552
Name     &gWestern Entrance from the Barrens&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The red, dry dust of the Barrens is suddenly cut short by a wall 
of thick, tangled vegetation. The path descends into a 
humid basin where the air is heavy with the scent of stagnant 
water and blooming night-lilies. A narrow, mud-slicked trail 
leads east into the Quagmire.
~
#EXIT
Direction out~
ToRoom    26650
Desc      Return to the southern Barrens.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    37553
Desc      The path leads into the swamp.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37515 10 37552
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37553
Name     &gThe Quagmire - Entrance&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The trees here are gnarled and covered in hanging moss, their 
roots twisting like snakes through the shallow water. Massive 
insects drone in the air, and the ground is soft and spongy 
underfoot.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    37552
Desc      The western entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    37554
Desc      The path continues east.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37505 5 37553
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37554
Name     &gThe Quagmire - Central&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The mist is thick here, obscuring the view of anything more 
than a few yards away. The only landmarks are the giant 
mushrooms and the occasional bleached rib-cage of some 
forgotten beast.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    37553
Desc      Western Quagmire.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    37555
Desc      Toward the village of Brackenwall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    37565
Desc      A path leads toward a small island.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37502 5 37554
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37555
Name     &gThe Quagmire - East&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The ground begins to rise slightly as the swamp gives way to 
a more solid stone path. To the east, the spiked wooden walls 
of a Horde outpost are visible through the fog.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    37554
Desc      Central Quagmire.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    37556
Desc      Entrance to Brackenwall Village.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37507 5 37555
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37556
Name     &rBrackenwall Village - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     Massive logs, sharpened to points, form the defensive walls of 
Brackenwall. Orc grunts stand firm at the gate, their axes 
gleaming in the soft marsh light.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    37555
Desc      Return to the swamp.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    37557
Desc      Brackenwall Town Square.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37501 5 37556
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37557
Name     &rBrackenwall - Town Square&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     The heart of the Horde's marsh outpost. A large bonfire 
burns in the center of the square, and several sturdy 
stone buildings provide shelter and supplies for the 
warriors stationed here.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    37556
Desc      The west gate.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37558
Desc      The Brackenwall Inn.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    37559
Desc      Overlord Mok'Morokk's Seat.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    37560
Desc      The Wyvern Roost.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 37530 5 37557
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37558
Name     &rThe Ogre's Kettle&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A warm, smoky inn that provides a welcome respite from the 
damp swamp air. The walls are decorated with trophies 
taken from the local raptors and turtles.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    37557
Desc      The square.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37559
Name     &rOverlord Mok'Morokk's Seat&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     A high stone platform overlooking the village. Overlord 
Mok'Morokk sits upon a massive, stolen chest, gnawing 
on a roasted haunch of kodo meat.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37557
Desc      The square.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37512 1 37559
  Reset G 1 37548 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37560
Name     &rBrackenwall - Wyvern Roost&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     A flat ledge at the highest point of the camp. Several 
wyverns rest here, ready to carry messages and warriors 
to Orgrimmar.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    37557
Desc      The square.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37561
Name     &gThe Shifting Bogs - North&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A treacherous expanse of deep, bubbling mud. Fallen trees 
provide a series of unstable bridges across the bogs, but 
one wrong step could lead to a slow, suffocating death.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    37562
Desc      The bogs continue south.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    37554
Desc      Return to the Quagmire.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37507 5 37561
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37562
Name     &gThe Shifting Bogs - South&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The trees are thinner here, but the mud is deeper. Small 
bubbles of swamp gas rise to the surface of the pools, 
bursting with a faint, sulfurous pop.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37561
Desc      The northern bogs.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    37563
Desc      Toward the eastern coast.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37518 5 37562
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37563
Name     &gThe Marshline Road&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A wide, stone road that has been partially reclaimed by the 
swamp. It leads east toward the Alliance stronghold of 
Theramore Isle.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    37562
Desc      The bogs.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    37567
Desc      The entrance to Theramore.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37500 5 37563
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37564
Name     &gThe Darkmist Caverns - Entrance&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large, web-choked cavern mouth in the northern mountains. 
The air is stagnant and smells of old decay and the 
metallic scent of spider-venom.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    37554
Desc      Return to the Quagmire.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37565
Desc      The webbed tunnels.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37506 5 37564
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37565
Name     &gThe Darkmist Tunnels&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls and ceiling are completely covered in thick, 
sticky white silk. Hundreds of small spiders skitter 
across the floor, following the vibrations of your footsteps.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    37564
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37566
Desc      The Widow's Chamber.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37524 10 37565
Reset O 0 37540 5 37565
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37566
Name     &gThe Darkmist Widow's Chamber&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive circular chamber. In the center, a gargantuan 
