web-wrapped cocoons—the remnants of unlucky travelers.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    37565
Desc      The tunnels.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37519 1 37566
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37567
Name     &BTheramore Isle - North Gate&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     The primary entrance to the Alliance stronghold. Massive 
