~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    37563
Desc      Return to the road.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    37568
Desc      Theramore Town Square.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37500 5 37567
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37568
Name     &BTheramore - Town Square&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     The center of the bustling island city. Soldiers and 
citizens move with purpose through the clean stone streets. 
A large fountain depicting the Crest of Lordaeron sits in 
