~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37567
Desc      The north gate.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    37569
Desc      The Theramore Inn.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    37571
Desc      The Keep of Jaina Proudmoore.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    37570
Desc      The Theramore Docks.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 37529 5 37568
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37569
Name     &BThe Anchor's Rest&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A warm, well-furnished inn built with the elegant 
craftsmanship of Kul Tiras. The air smells of pine 
