~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    37568
Desc      The square.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37570
Name     &BTheramore - Main Docks&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     A massive stone pier jutting into the Veiled Sea. Elegant 
