~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    37568
Desc      The square.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37571
Name     &BThe Tower of Lady Jaina Proudmoore&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The heart of Theramore's leadership. Lady Jaina Proudmoore 
