~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37568
Desc      The square.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37511 1 37571
  Reset G 1 37538 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37572
Name     &gThe Mirefin Strand - North&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A long, sandy beach stretching along the northern coast. 
Murloc huts made of seaweed and driftwood line the shore, 
and the air is filled with the sound of gurgling cries.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    37573
Desc      The strand continues south.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    37553
Desc      Return to the Quagmire.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37503 10 37572
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37573
Name     &gThe Mirefin Strand - South&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The beach widens here, meeting the edge of the deep swamp. 
Murloc oracles can be seen performing rituals in the 
shallow surf, calling upon the power of the sea.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37572
Desc      The northern strand.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37523 5 37573
Reset O 0 37526 10 37573
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37574
Name     &gThe Wyrmbog - Entrance&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The vegetation becomes more sparse and charred as you approach 
the southern bogs. The air is warm and smells of sulfur 
