~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37563
Desc      Return to the road.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    37575
Desc      Deep into the Wyrmbog.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37508 5 37574
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37575
Name     &gDeep Wyrmbog - Center&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The heart of the Black Dragonflight's territory in Dustwallow. 
Massive, obsidian-scaled drakes circle overhead, and the 
ground is littered with the charred bones of intruders.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37574
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    37576
Desc      Toward the Dragonmurk.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37520 5 37575
Reset O 0 37531 10 37575
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37576
Name     &gThe Dragonmurk Ridge&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A high stone ridge overlooking the southern marshes. From 
here, you can see the smoking entrance to the dragon lair. 
Onyxian whelps play in the warm updrafts rising from the pools.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37575
Desc      The central Wyrmbog.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    37590
Desc      The Dragonmurk Mouth (Portal to Onyxia's Lair).~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37510 10 37576
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37590
Name     &rThe Dragonmurk Mouth&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You stand before the massive, jagged entrance to the lair of 
Onyxia, the Broodmother. The air is blistering hot, and 
the ground is composed of solid, black glass. A shimmering, 
fiery portal glows within the deep cavern.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37576
Desc      Return to the ridge.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37577
Name     &gTabetha's Farm - Entrance&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A small, well-tended clearing in the deep marsh. A humble 
