several strange, magical gardens.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    37562
Desc      Return to the bogs.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37578
Desc      Tabetha's Hut.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 37513 1 37577
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     37578
Name     &gTabetha's Hut&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The interior of the hut is filled with bookshelves and 
